msgstr "Dayami ng Pari"

# Mandar constellation, native: Bittoéng Sapo Kepang
msgid "Slanted House"
msgstr "Slanted House"

# Description of Mandar constellation Slanted House
msgid "Used as an indicator for the south."
msgstr "Ginamit bilang isang tagapagpahiwatig para sa timog."

# Description of Mandar constellation Shark
msgid "Marks the entry of the northwest monsoon season."
msgstr "Minarkahan ang pagpasok ng hilagang-kanlurang tag-ulan."

# Mandar constellation, native: Bittoéng Lambaru
msgid "Stingray"
msgstr "Stingray"

# Description of Mandar constellation Stingray
msgid "Marks the entry of the northwest monsoon season, like the Shark."
msgstr ""
"Minamarkahan ang pagpasok ng hilagang-kanlurang tag-ulan, tulad ng Shark."

# Mandar constellation, native: Bittoéng Panjala
msgid "Fishing Net"
msgstr "Pangingisda Net"

# Description of Mandar constellation Fishing Net
msgid ""
"Used as an indicator of the entry of the cool season (between the two "
"monsoons) and the emergence of the bambang fish."
msgstr ""
"Ginamit bilang tagapagpahiwatig ng pagpasok ng malamig na panahon (sa "
"pagitan ng dalawang tag-ulan) at ang paglitaw ng bambang isda."

# Mandar constellation, native: Bittoéng Tallu-tallu
msgid "Group of Three Stars"
msgstr "Grupo ng Tatlong Bituin"

# Description of Mandar constellation Group of Three Stars
msgid "Used as a mark towards the east from the Pleiades (Bittoéng Malunus)."
msgstr ""
"Ginamit bilang isang marka patungo sa silangan mula sa Pleiades (Bittoéng "
"Malunus)."

# Mandar constellation, native: Bittoéng Tuwallu
msgid "Widow"
msgstr "Balo"

# Description of Mandar constellation Widow
msgid ""
"Used as an indicator for the south, like the Slanted House. It is not clear "
"whether the stars should be linked by a line or not."
msgstr ""
"Ginamit bilang indicator para sa timog, tulad ng Slanted House. Hindi "
"malinaw kung ang mga bituin ay dapat iugnay sa pamamagitan ng isang linya o "
"hindi."

